patthana8.23:1.1_0: Nasaññojanañceva naasaññojaniyañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nasaññojano ceva naasaññojaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.23:1.1_1: Nasaññojanañceva naasaññojaniyañca dhammaṁ paṭicca naasaññojaniyo ceva nanoasaññojano ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.23:1.1_2: Nasaññojanañceva naasaññojaniyañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nasaññojano ceva naasaññojaniyo ca naasaññojaniyo ceva nano ca saññojano ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana8.23:2.1_0: Naasaññojaniyañceva nano ca saññojanaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naasaññojaniyo ceva nano ca saññojano dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.23:3.1_0: Nasaññojanañceva naasaññojaniyañca naasaññojaniyañceva nanosaññojanañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nasaññojano ceva naasaññojaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.23:4.1_0: Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe nava …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate nava. (Sabbattha vitthāro.)
